title: Sygic OpenStreetMap 3D buildings addon
description:
Add more detailed landmarks and buildings to your Sygic maps with this simple tool from OpenStreetMap 3D buildings 


Step 1)
Ensure you have the map installed in Sygic already

Step 2)
Run this executable, and select the region then country you want

Step 3)
Once finished, you will now have an "xx.2dc" file where you just ran the exe file

step 3)
Copy this xx.2dc file into your phone: /sygic/maps/xx.ta.2015.xx/ making sure you overwrite the existing one.

See how the new file is much larger than the existing one? This is because it's full of super detailed 3d buildings.

Enjoy


FlamerFTW
